Operators are encouraged to develop their own 'quick reference' normal checklists based on the procedures provided in this manual. The sequence of individual checklist items should sub sub bar emphasis-bold not be changed when operator-specific quick reference checklists are developed. For example, turning off the autofeather system is listed as the last item in the After Takeoff checklist, and it should remain the last item in any operator-specific 'quick reference' After Takeoff checklist.
